{"type": "article", "id": 21413, "title": "需要调配的巧克力", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-28T07:32:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164747JRkVynlxz3tDLiwQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tnendo 设计的这组巧克力包装将化学实验的风格带了进来，五种不同颜色和形状的巧克力被装进了 5 个很小的玻璃试管里，下面有 4 个像圆底烧瓶一样的小瓶子。它引导了一种吃巧克力的方式，将不同的巧克力按照自己喜欢的比例混合装进瓶子里。经过自己调配后的巧克力增加了一份个性，也能让你更开心吧。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/chocolamixture-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150937c5JlLFWDyC4Okhpv.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150937wcV205u17tTMq94r.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150938pVxYja0MiOGQy4DE.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150938tIvXC6mn2xq9shy7.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}